description: Share your photos Let's you share your photos on the Lut.im server of your choice. Use your own server to regain control of your privacy! * Multiple configurable hosting URLs -- Use your own server! * Copy the sharing URL to clipboard or share it to another application * Keep track of your storage lifetime * HTTP & HTTPS support * Share history with thumbnails, share control. * Encryption of images on the server For additional information on the client and server part, visite the project page.
